Package main.java.generator

This package is concerned with creating and solving Sudoku Boards.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Generator
    A Generator to generate random Sudoku Grid instances.
    Grid
    This class represents a Sudoku Grid consisting of a 9x9 matrix containing nine 3x3 sub-grids of Grid.Cells.
    Grid.Cell
    This class represents a Cell within a Sudoku Grid.
    Solver
    A Solver is capable of solving a given Sudoku Grid.

Package main.java.generator Description

This package is concerned with creating and solving Sudoku Boards. Of note, the Generator can create boards given the number of free spaces desired, and the Solver will solve a Sudoku Grid In-Place.
